'''三星Galaxy Tab S7'''及'''Galaxy Tab S7+'''是兩款由[[三星電子|三星電子]]設計、開發及銷售，並搭載[[Android|Android]]系統的[[三星Galaxy_S系列|三星Galaxy S系列]][[平板電腦|平板電腦]]產品。有關產品於2020年8月5日在三星的線上Unpacked活動中亮相。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Meet Galaxy Tab S7 and S7+: Your Perfect Companion to Work, Play and More|url=https://news.samsung.com/us/galaxy-tab-s7-plus-unpacked-2020/|accessdate=2020-08-14|publisher=''Samsung Newsroom US''|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130033905/https://news.samsung.com/us/galaxy-tab-s7-plus-unpacked-2020/}}</ref>

== 設計 ==
三星Galaxy Tab S7及Tab S7+大致維持上代的設計，但採用較大的顯示螢幕。當中11吋型號取代舊有10.5吋型號，另亦推出新的12.4吋型號。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Meet Galaxy Tab S7 and S7+: Your Perfect Companion to Work, Play and More|url=https://news.samsung.com/global/meet-galaxy-tab-s7-and-s7-plus-your-perfect-companion-to-work-play-and-more|accessdate=2020-08-27|publisher=''news.samsung.com''|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128060140/https://news.samsung.com/global/meet-galaxy-tab-s7-and-s7-plus-your-perfect-companion-to-work-play-and-more}}</ref>兩款產品均備有三種全新顏色選項，分別為{{hover title|Mystic Black|霧光黑}}、{{hover title|Mystic Silver|霧光銀}}及{{hover title|Mystic Bronze|霧光銅}}。<ref name=":0" />

== 技術規格 ==
=== 硬件 ===
==== 顯示屏 ====
Galaxy Tab S7採用11吋2560×1600解像度的[[液晶显示器|LCD顯示屏]]<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Samsung Galaxy Tab S7 - Full tablet specifications|url=https://www.gsmarena.com/samsung_galaxy_tab_s7-10337.php|accessdate=2020-08-27|work=''www.gsmarena.com''|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925234728/https://www.gsmarena.com/samsung_galaxy_tab_s7-10337.php}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Samsung announces the Galaxy Tab S7 and S7 Plus, Android tablet built to get work done|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/samsung-announces-the-galaxy-tab-s7-and-s7-plus-android-tablet-built-to-get-work-done/|accessdate=2020-08-27|last=Cipriani|first=Jason|work=''ZDNet''|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210521120120/https://www.zdnet.com/article/samsung-announces-the-galaxy-tab-s7-and-s7-plus-android-tablet-built-to-get-work-done/}}</ref>，而Tab S7+則配備12.4吋2800×1752解像度的[[有機發光二極體|OLED]]顯示屏（廠方稱之為「Super AMOLED」）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Samsung Galaxy Tab S7+ - Full tablet specifications|url=https://www.gsmarena.com/samsung_galaxy_tab_s7+-10336.php|accessdate=2020-08-27|work=''www.gsmarena.com''|archive-date=2021-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210531225056/https://www.gsmarena.com/samsung_galaxy_tab_s7+-10336.php}}</ref>。兩者均提供120 Hz螢幕更新率。<ref name=":1" />

==== 晶片 ====
兩款產品均採用高通驍龍865+[[单片系统|单片系统]]，為一片基於[[7纳米制程|7 nm+]]製程技術的處理器。產品亦配備一枚型號為[[Adreno|Adreno]] 650的圖像處理器（GPU）。<ref name=":1" />

==== 內部儲存 ====
兩款產品設有128、256及512 GB內部儲存選項<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Samsung Galaxy Tab S7, Galaxy Tab S7+ With 120Hz Display Launched in India|url=https://gadgets.ndtv.com/tablets/news/samsung-tab-s7-plus-price-in-india-rs-55999-galaxy-launch-specifications-features-2285583|accessdate=2020-08-27|work=''NDTV Gadgets 360''|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507231304/https://gadgets.ndtv.com/tablets/news/samsung-tab-s7-plus-price-in-india-rs-55999-galaxy-launch-specifications-features-2285583}}</ref>（部份地區或未必提供所有選項），亦可透過microSD卡擴充最多1 TB空間；另亦配備6 GB[[随机存取存储器|随机存取存储器]]，並可升級至8 GB。

==== 電池 ====
Galaxy Tab S7及Tab S7+均採用不可拆除的[[鋰離子聚合物電池|鋰離子聚合物]]電池，容量分別為8000mAh及10090mAh。<ref name=":2" />兩款產品亦支援45W快速充電。

==== 連接性 ====
縱然部份地區或提供[[長期演進技術|LTE]]或sub-6GHz型號，兩款產品均支援[[5G|5G]]連線<ref>{{Cite web|title=Samsung Galaxy Tab S7 & S7+ {{!}} Samsung US|url=https://www.samsung.com/us/tablets/tab-s7/|accessdate=2020-08-27|work=''The Official Samsung Galaxy Site''|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210611054014/https://www.samsung.com/us/tablets/tab-s7/}}</ref>；另亦提供Wi-Fi型號。

==== 鏡頭 ====
兩款產品均配備雙後置鏡頭<ref>{{Cite web|title=Samsung Galaxy Tab S7 Plus Initial Review - Stunning iPad Pro alternative|url=https://www.xda-developers.com/samsung-galaxy-tab-s7-plus-preview/|accessdate=2020-08-27|date=2020-08-26|work=''xda-developers''|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301230920/https://www.xda-developers.com/samsung-galaxy-tab-s7-plus-preview/}}</ref>，當中廣角鏡為一支26毫米、1300萬像素（f/2.0）的鏡頭，而超廣角鏡為一支12毫米、500萬像素（f/2.2）的鏡頭。<ref name=":1" />

==== S-Pen ====
兩款產品均支援較佳的延遲（9毫秒），與[[三星Galaxy_Note_20|三星Galaxy Note 20]]相似<ref name=":2" />，並支援全新Air手勢。

=== 軟件 ===
Galaxy Tab S7及Tab S7+均預裝基於[[Android_10|Android 10]]的[[One_UI|One UI 2]]，並支援[[三星DeX|三星DeX]]。

